					Full Description



		Petrolina Holdings Public Ltd is a Cyprus-based commercial enterprise engaged in the petrochemicals field. Its activities include the import and trade of motor, industrial, domestic, marine and aviation fuels, Liquefied Petroleum Gas (LPG), lubricants, greases and other related products. Its fuel products include agriculture diesel, aviation gasoline, biodiesel, bitumen, diesel, heating/industrial gasoil, heavy fuel oil, illuminating kerosene and jet A1 among other. Its lubricants comprise engine oils, such as motorcycle and outboard, marine, and automotive engine oils; automotive gear oils, and industrial and automotive greases among other. The Company is also active in the supply of aircraft fuel through its subsidiary, PPT Aviation Services Ltd, which operates at Larnaca and Paphos airports and in the blending of lubricants through its subsidiary, Superlube Ltd. The Company has a retail network of 95 service stations throughout Cyprus, supplying various industrial clients.
» Full Overview of PHLEUR.MIp







