Company Overview of Petrolina (Holdings) Public Ltd



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Petrolina (Holdings) Public Ltd, a petroleum company, engages in the purchase, importation, storage, and sale of petroleum products in Cyprus. The company markets consumer and local businesses with automobile and heating fuels, fuels for industrial use, marine and aviation fuels, motor fuels, and other related products, as well as liquefied petroleum gas and bitumen. In addition, it produces lubricants, as well as provides aviation refueling and bunkering services. The company operates a network of 100 service stations under the Petrolina and Agip brand names. Petrolina (Holdings) Public Ltd was founded in 1959 and is based in Larnaca, Cyprus.


Kilkis 1Larnaca,  6015CyprusFounded in 1959



Phone: 357 2 4848000

Fax: 357 2 4657173

www.petrolina.com.cy







